item.description: File: Untitled document(193).txt # She wanted to keep going. She wanted to be the strongest ever. She wanted to see things through. She wanted to be who she needed to be. She wanted to be the best she needed to be. She wanted to be easier. She wanted to make things perfect. She wanted everything to be beautiful. She wanted everything to be beautiful. She wanted to ruin the people and their decisions, meanwhile her friends died in the back.
